msgid "Viewing relationships"
msgstr "查看关系"

msgid "Viewing relationships between physical servers and virtual hosts"
msgstr "查看物理服务器与虚拟主机之间的关系"

msgid ""
"CloudForms shows relationships between virtual host systems and physical "
"servers and the virtual hosts for each physical-infrastructure provider. The "
"topology view provides a graphical representation of the relationships, "
"allowing you to easily navigate between connected nodes (see the following "
"figure)."
msgstr ""
"CloudForms "
