msgstr "从<emphasis role=\"strong\">选择</emphasis>列表中，选中想要分配给配置集的服务器的复选框。"

msgid "Step 3. Configure the alert associated with the alert profile"
msgstr "第 3 步：配置与警告配置集关联的警告"

msgid ""
"Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Alert Profiles &gt; Physical Server Alert "
"Profiles &gt; <emphasis>ProfileName</emphasis> &gt; Physical server has "
"critical health state</emphasis>, where <emphasis>ProfileName</emphasis> is "
"the name of the physical server alert profile that was previously created."
msgstr ""
"单击<emphasis role=\"strong\">警告配置集 &gt; 物理服务器警告配置集 &gt; "
"<emphasis>ProfileName</emphasis> &gt; 物理服务器存在关键健康状态</emphasis>，其中 "
"<emphasis>ProfileName</emphasis> 是之前创建的物理服务器警告配置集的名称。"

msgid ""
"Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Configuration &gt; Edit this Alert</"
